name: Womens CAMPPAIN Boobies shirt
description: No matter where your eyes are this shirt will make sure people pay attention. What's not to like, the human body is a beautiful thing. Accentuate yours with our Boobies "T"! Features dual CAMPPAIN logos on the front, signature "CP" logo on the right sleeve, and of course a special custom tagless neck logo! Printed on 100% American Apparel shirts!

The shirts are printed on American Apparel 100% cotton tees which are made in America and printed here in the good ol' US of A!
